Thanks for my Saturday political satire fix.I have been following this election in the US.Not many politicians have any answers to problems so they resort to making their opponents look bad and scare tactics.They do this thinking the voters are idiots.They may be right.It comes down to who makes the least gaffes not to who is the best candidate.This gives Bill lots of fodder for his t.v. show.
